Maaddaama aysan jirin daaweyn gaar ah oo COVID-19 ah, TCM ayaa ah mid ka mid ah daaweynta ugu muhiimsan ee loogu talagalay bukaannada qaba calaamadaha fudud ama dhexdhexaadka ah ama ka baxsan noocyada daran ee cudurka.
