Si kastaba ha ahaatee, waxtarka in vivo ee tallaaladaas la filayo ee dadka da'da ah iyo moodooyinka la dilay iyo ka hortagga cudurka fayraska zoonotic ayaa weli la ogaanayaa, maadaama aan wali la bilaabin daraasad caafimaad.
