Ururka Caafimaadka Adduunka ayaa COVID-19 ku tilmaamay cudur faafa
Arbacadii, Ururka Caafimaadka Adduunka (WHO) wuxuu ku tilmaamay faafitaanka COVID-19 (cudur ay keento coronavirus SARS-CoV-2) inuu yahay cudur faafa.
Inkastoo erayga  faafida  uu la xiriiro kaliya heerka faafitaanka cudurka, oo aan la tixgelin halista kiisaska gaarka ah, WHO waxay tilmaamtay baahida loo qabo in dowladaha la dhaqaajiyo:
 Wadamada oo dhan weli way badali karaan wadada cudurkan faafa.
