bLenzyme of angiotensin conversion 2 (ACE2) waa enzyme ku xidhan dhinaca dibedda (membranes cell) ee unugyada sanbabada, wadnaha, kelyaha iyo mindhicirka.
LACE2 waxay ka hortagtaa waxqabadka enzyme-ka beddelashada angiotensin (ACE) iyadoo la yareynayo xaddiga angiotensin II iyo kordhinta Ang (1-7), taas oo ka dhigaysa bartilmaameed daawo oo rajo leh daaweynta cudurada wadnaha. LACE2 sidoo kale waa barta laga galo unugyada qaar ka mid ah coronavirus-yada.
Nooca aadanaha ee enzyme-ka waxaa badanaa loo yaqaan hACE2.
Angiotensin 2 conversion enzyme waa metallosymmetric zinc-ka ku jira oo ku yaal dusha sare ee unugyada endothelial iyo unugyada kale.
Borotiinka ACE2 wuxuu leeyahay domain N-terminal peptidase M2 iyo domain C-terminal renal amino acid transporter colectrin.
LACE2 waa protein-ka nooc I ah oo leh hal-mar-mar-mar-mar-mar ah, oo domain-ka firfircoon ee enzymatic-ka uu ku yaal dusha sare ee unugyada sanbabada iyo unugyada kale.
Aagga ka baxsan unugyada ee ACE2 waxaa laga soo saaraa unugyada transmembrane by enzyme kale oo loo yaqaan sheddase; protein-ka la milmi karo ee ka dhasha waxaa loo sii daayaa dhiiga ugu dambeyntii waxaa lagu soo saaraa kaadida.
LACE2 waxay ku jirtaa xubnaha badankood: LACE2 waxay ku xiran tahay xuubka unugyada inta badan unugyada alveoliga sambabada nooca II, enterocytes-ka mindhicirka yar, unugyada endothelial ee xididka iyo xididka iyo unugyada xididka ee muruqyada jilicsan ee xubnaha badankood.
Isbeddelka mRNA ee ACE2 wuxuu sidoo kale ka jiraa qanjirka maskaxda, xididdada, hypothalamus iyo jirka maskaxda.
Shaqada ugu horeysa ee ACE2 waa in ay ka dhigan tahay ACE.
ACE waxay ka soo saarta angiotensin I hormoonkeeda oo loo yaqaan angiotensin II oo ah xakameyn xidid.
LACE2 waxay u kala qaybisay amino acidka phenyl-amino acid ee carboxyl-terminated ee angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) iyo hydrolysis angiotensin vasodilator (1-7), (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
LACE2 waxay sidoo kale kala goyn kartaa dhowr peptides oo kale oo ay ka mid yihiin [des-Arg9]-bradykinin, lapelin, neurotensin, dynorphine A, iyo ghrelin.
LACE2 waxay sidoo kale xakameysaa wareegga xuubka ee SLC6A19 oo ah isgaarsiinta amino acid ee dhexdhexaad ah waxayna ku lug leedahay cudurka Hartnup.
Sida borotiinka xarkaha, ACE2 waa meesha ugu weyn ee laga galo unugyada qaar ka mid ah coronavirus-yada, oo ay ku jiraan HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (viruska keena SARS); iyo SARS-CoV-2 (viruska keena COVID-19).
Gaar ahaan, isku xirnaanta borotiinka S1 ee SARS-CoV iyo SARS-CoV2 ee la xiriira aagga enzymatic ee ACE2 ee dusha sare ee unugyada waxay keentaa endocytosis iyo translocation labadaba fayraska iyo enzyme-ka gudaha unugyada.
Geedi socodka soo galitaanka waxaa sidoo kale u baahan in la bilaabo protein S-ka oo ay ku jirto TMPRSS2 ee ka hortagga protease-ka ee martida u ah, waxaana hadda la baarayaa sida daaweyn la doonayo.
Si kastaba ha ahaatee, dhowr hay'adood oo xirfadlayaal ah iyo hay'ado sharciyeed ayaa ku taliyey in la sii wado daaweynta caadiga ah ee ACE inhibitor iyo ARB.
Baadhitaan nidaamsan iyo falanqayn meta oo la daabacay 11 Luulyo 2012 ayaa muujisay in isticmaalka ACE inhibitors ay la xiriirtay yareyn 34% ah oo ah khatarta ah in uu jiro pneumonia marka la barbardhigo kuwa la xakameynayo. 
Intaa waxaa dheer, khatarta ah in uu jiro cudurka sambabada ayaa sidoo kale hoos u dhacay bukaanada la daaweeyay ACE inhibitor kuwaas oo khatar sare ugu jiray cudurka sambabada, gaar ahaan kuwa la ildaran wadnaha iyo wadnaha oo aan ku guuleysan.
Isticmaalka ACE inhibitors waxaa sidoo kale lala xiriiriyay dhimashada dhimashada cudurka sambabada, inkastoo natiijooyinka aan la hubin marka loo eego halista wadarta sambabada. 
Human recombinant angiotensin 2 (rhACE2) converting enzyme waxaa loo arkaa inay tahay daaweyn cusub oo loogu talagalay dhaawaca sambabka ee daran, waxayna u muuqataa inay hagaajineyso haemo-daynamiga sambabka iyo oksijiinta ku-dheelitirka ee doofaarka qaba cudurka neefsashada oo adag ee lipopolysaccharide-ka.
Nolosha nuska ah ee rhACE2 ee aadanaha waa qiyaastii 10 saacadood, waqtiga waxqabadkuna waa 30 daqiiqo marka lagu daro waqtiga waxqabadka (mudada) ee 24 saacadood.
Dhowr natiijo ayaa muujinaya in rhACE2 uu noqon karo daawo rajo leh dadka aan u dulqaadan karin xannibaadaha nidaamka renin-angiotensin (RAI) ama cudurada ay ku badan tahay wareegga angiotensin II. RhACE2 oo la buufiyo ayaa lagu qiimeeyay tijaabooyinka caafimaad ee daaweynta cudurka neefsashada oo daran.
