Bishii Maarso, Ururka Caafimaadka Adduunka ayaa bilaabay tijaabada SOLIDARITY si loo qiimeeyo saamaynta daaweynta ee afar ka mid ah daawooyinka ka hortagga fayraska ee jira oo leh waxtarka ugu badan.
