Istaraatiijiyad saddexaad waa tallaalada ku saleysan nucleic acid (tallaalka DNA ama RNA, farsamo cusub oo lagu abuuro tallaalka).
Talaalada tijaabada ah ee laga helo dhammaan xeeladahaas ayaa la filayaa in lagu tijaabiyo badbaadada iyo waxtarka. 16 Maarso 2020, tijaabada ugu horreysa ee bukaan socodka ee tallaalka ayaa ka bilaabatay afar mutadawiciin ah oo ku sugan Seattle.
