Falanqaynta horumarinta caafimaad ee talaalka iyo daawooyinka COVID-19 ee la doonayo ayaa sidoo kale la sameeyay bishii Abriil 2020. Daawooyin badan oo ka hortagga fayraska ayaa lagu qiimeynayaa daaweynta COVID-19, oo ay ku jiraan remdesivir, chloroquine iyo hydroxychloroquine, lopinavir/ritonavir, iyo lopinavir/ritonavir oo ay weheliso interferon beta.
